    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali45-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu varaiviṭai yāṟṟāta talaivikkut tōḻi tāṉ talaivaṉai neruṅki varaivukaṭāva 
            atukēṭṭa talaivaṉ varaivumuyaṟciyāṉ varutal iṭaiyiṭṭatūun tamar varai vetirntatūuṅ kūṟi avaḷai āṟṟuvittatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"/>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali45">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>viṭiyalveṅ katirkāyum vēyama lakalaṟaik</l>
                <l>kaṭicuṉaik kaviṉiya kāntaḷaṅ kulaiyiṉai</l>
                <l>yarumaṇi yavirutti yaravunī ruṇalcettup</l>
                <l>perumalai miḷirppaṉṉa kāṟṟuṭaik kaṉaipeya</l>
                <l>lurumukkaṇ ṇuṟutali ṉuyarkura loliyōṭi</l>
                <l>naṟuvīya naṉañcāraṟ cilampaliṟ katumeṉac</l>
                <l>ciṟukuṭi tuyileḻūuñ cēṇuyar viṟalveṟpa;</l>
                <l rend="space">kālpora nuṭaṅkaliṟ kaṟaṅkicai yaruviniṉ</l>
                <l>mālvarai malicuṉai malarēykku meṉpatō</l>
                <l>pullārāp puṇarcciyāṟ pulampiya veṉṟōḻi</l>
                <l>pallitaḻ malaruṇkaṇ pacappanī citaittatai;</l>
                <l rend="space">pukarmukak kaḷiṟoṭu puliporu tuḻakkuniṉ</l>
                <l>ṉakaṉmalai yaṭukkatta vamaiyēykku meṉpatō</l>
                <l>kaṭaiyeṉak kaluḻunōy kaimmika veṉṟōḻi</l>
                <l>taṭaiyiṉa tiraṇṭatōḷ takaivāṭac citaittatai;</l>
                <l rend="space">cuṭaruṟa vuṟanīṇṭa curumpimi raṭukkatta</l>
                <l>viṭarvarai yerivēṅkai yiṇarēykku meṉpatō</l>
                <l>yāmattun tuyilala ḷalamaru meṉṟōḻi</l>
                <l>kāmaru nalleḻil kaviṉvāṭac citaittatai;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku.</l>
                <l>taṉṟīmai palakūṟik kaḻaṟali ṉeṉṟōḻi</l>
                <l>maṟaiyiṟṟāṉ maruvuṟa maṇantanaṭ parukalāṟ</l>
                <l>piṟaipurai nutalavarp pēṇinam</l>
                <l>muṟaivarain taṉarava ruvakku nāḷē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="7cd">            O man from the victorious mountain high in the distance, where </l>
<l corresp="3">the snake with hood spots that shine [like] precious sapphires takes for water to drink </l>
<l corresp="2">the bunches of Malabar lilies that beautified the protected pool </l>
<l corresp="1">in the wide rocks dense with bamboo which hot rays burn at dawn, </l>
<l corresp="5ab+d">runs, because of fearing the mere sight of the thunder </l>
<l corresp="4+5c">with intense rain with wind as if the big mountain was rolling, before the sound of the high voice</l>
<l corresp="7ab">[and] raises the little hamlet from sleep, </l>
<l corresp="6">quickly, because of it resounding on the vast slope with fragrant blossoms, </l>
<l rend="space">It says “it resembles the blossoms in the ample pool of your large mountain </l>
<l>with waterfalls noisy with sound, because they sway when the wind dashes”,</l>
<l>about what you spoil when the kajal eyes of my friend become pale, blossoms </l>
<l>with many petals, that are lonely because of the mean unsatisfactory union.</l>
<l rend="space">It says “it resembles the bamboo on the slope of your wide mountain</l>
<l>where the tiger fought with [and] destroyed the elephant bull with spotted face”,</l>
<l>about what [you] spoil when the fitness of my friend’s plump round shoulders fades</l>
<l>as pain exceeds when she weeps “[this is] the end”.</l>
<l rend="space">It says “it resembles the clusters of the flaming kino tree on the clefted mountain</l>
<l>with slopes where bees hum who delay while they keeps enjoying the [sun’s] glow,”</l>
<l>about what [you] spoil when the lovely good graceful beauty of my friend pales</l>
<l>who is upset, being one without sleep even at midnight.</l>
<l rend="space">That is to say,</l>
<l rend="space">because of [my] grumbling, talking many [words] about his faults,</l>
<l>he will not withhold the intimacy in which he united, so as to have union in secret with my friend.</l>
<l>They will honour [her] forehead [as] resembling the crescent moon </l>
<l>[and] marry [her off] in our residence on the day they rejoice.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
